<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #DC2626; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .footer { background-color: #333; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .warning-box { background-color: #FEE2E2; border-left: 4px solid #DC2626; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .info-box { background-color: #FEF3C7; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #DC2626; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; }
        .button:hover { background-color: #B91C1C; }
        .button-secondary { display: inline-block; background-color: #6B7280; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px 5px; font-weight: bold; }
        .button-secondary:hover { background-color: #4B5563; }
        .details { background-color: white; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; }
        .details p { margin: 8px 0; }
        .icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .reasons { background-color: white; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #FCA5A5; }
        .reasons ul { margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; }
        .reasons li { margin: 5px 0; color: #991B1B; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="icon">âœ—</div>
            <h1 style="margin: 0;">KYC Verification Not Approved</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{organizationName}},</p>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <h2 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #991B1B;">Verification Status Update</h2>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px;">We regret to inform you that your KYC (Know Your Customer) verification application was not approved at this time.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="details">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1F2937;">Application Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Organization:</strong> {{organizationName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Application ID:</strong> {{applicationId}}</p>
                <p><strong>Submission Date:</strong> {{submittedDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Review Date:</strong> {{reviewedDate}}</p>
            </div>

            {{#if rejectionReasons}}
            <div class="reasons">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #991B1B;">Reasons for Non-Approval</h3>
                <p>Your application was not approved due to the following reason(s):</p>
                <ul>
                    {{#each rejectionReasons}}
                    <li>{{this}}</li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #92400E;">What You Can Do</h3>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;">You can resubmit your KYC application after addressing the issues mentioned above:</p>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0;">
                    <li>Review and correct any incorrect or incomplete information</li>
                    <li>Provide clear, high-quality copies of required documents</li>
                    <li>Ensure all documents are current and not expired</li>
                    <li>Verify that document details match your registration information</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{resubmitUrl}}" class="button">Resubmit Application</a>
                <br>
                <a href="{{supportUrl}}" class="button-secondary">Contact Support</a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px; background-color: #E0F2FE; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6;">
                <strong>Need Help?</strong><br>
                Our support team is available to assist you with the resubmission process. Please don't hesitate to reach out if you have any questions or need clarification on the required documents.
            </p>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">We appreciate your understanding and look forward to helping you complete the verification process successfully.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px;">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong>The CitadelBuy Compliance Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>CitadelBuy</strong> - Secure E-Commerce Platform</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0;">Need assistance? Contact us at {{supportEmail}}</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0;">&copy; {{currentYear}} CitadelBuy. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0; font-size: 11px;">
                This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
